*NAME&
        secterm - interface for OpenSecurity's Security Terminal block

*SYNOPSIS
        secterm ?action& [?param&]

*DESCRIPTION&
        This utility provides a command-line interface for the *Security Terminal& block added by OpenSecurity.

        *secterm& accepts the following ?action&s:

            *setpass&
                Sets the Security Terminal's password.

            *add ?user&
                Adds the specified ?user& to the terminal's list of allowed users.
